				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/C%E1%BB%AB-Kh%C3%AA-th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-lIvsZGniDW6RNofQBU3cXA">Cừ Khê thảo đường kỳ 2 - 渠溪草堂其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/X%C3%A0-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/%C4%90i%E1%BB%87u-n%E1%BB%99i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-tg7h6HxOBZENJ1Y8CasBcw">Điệu nội kỳ 2 - 悼内其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/X%C3%A0-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-OTOkL6TRbM0V41YwHIzvfA">Xà Tường</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%BD-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-s%C6%A1n-nh%C3%A2n-B%C6%B0u-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-4X_OGP73GJDCNDZGVQ_DbA">Ký Trương thập nhị sơn nhân Bưu tam thập vận - 寄張十二山人彪三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1ng-T%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-6DNxT26SOJCO6AUWxHaKrQ">Sơn hành - 山行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1ng-T%C6%B0/author-06eZNa3RWYuOvqTqvYb-Gw">Hạng Tư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%C3%A2y-giang-nguy%E1%BB%87t-Ho%E1%BA%A1-L%E1%BA%ADt-Vi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn-gi%E1%BA%A3n-Ho%C3%A0-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-N7OvClQ3hI34f-YEciy1Kg">Tây giang nguyệt - Hoạ Lật Viên vận giản Hoà Phủ - 西江月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Nh%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BB%95/Th%C3%A0nh-nam-vi%C3%AAn-c%C6%B0/poem-NrzfbA3gteXZ9mWM1gvY9w">Thành nam viên cư - 城南園居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Nh%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BB%95/author-66ia4YCzwE1fNYpyqsHF2Q">Nguyễn Như Đổ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Th%C3%B4n-c%C6%B0-S%E1%BB%95-duy%C3%AAn-th%C6%B0-th%E1%BA%A5t-y%E1%BB%83m-b%E1%BB%93ng-cao/poem-VefbNoKo_0HbRKOmvtOvow">Thôn cư (Sổ duyên thư thất yểm bồng cao) - 村居（數椽書室掩蓬筸）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-24/poem-rrYJZBWukSn78Tnyz4BNFw">Thủ 24 - 首２４</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-thanh/poem-Rwzk5TA0EUH4XzgzgIxIYA">Thu thanh - 秋清</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
